#. <section class="sutta" id="sn48.44"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn48.44:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 48"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 48"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn48.44:0.2"
msgid "5. Jarāvagga"
msgstr "5. Old Age"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn48.44:0.3"
msgid "44. Pubbakoṭṭhakasutta"
msgstr "44. At the Eastern Gate"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn48.44:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—​"
msgstr "So I have heard."

msgctxt "sn48.44:1.2"
msgid "ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati pubbakoṭṭhake."
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying in Sāvatthī at the eastern gate."

msgctxt "sn48.44:1.3"
msgid "Tatra kho bhagavā āyasmantaṃ sāriputtaṃ āmantesi:"
msgstr "Then the Buddha said to Venerable Sāriputta:"

#. VAR: saddahasi → saddahāsi (bj, pts1)
msgctxt "sn48.44:1.4"
msgid "“saddahasi tvaṃ, sāriputta—"
msgstr "“Sāriputta, do you have faith that"

msgctxt "sn48.44:1.5"
msgid ""
"saddhindriyaṃ bhāvitaṃ bahulīkataṃ amatogadhaṃ hoti amataparāyaṇaṃ "
"amatapariyosānaṃ … pe … paññindriyaṃ bhāvitaṃ bahulīkataṃ amatogadhaṃ hoti "
"amataparāyaṇaṃ amatapariyosānan”ti?"
msgstr ""
"the faculties of faith, energy, mindfulness, immersion, and wisdom, when "
"developed and cultivated, culminate, finish, and end in the deathless?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli5.221"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn48.44:2.1"
msgid "“Na khvāhaṃ ettha, bhante, bhagavato saddhāya gacchāmi—"
msgstr "“Sir, in this case I don’t rely on faith in the Buddha’s claim that"

msgctxt "sn48.44:2.2"
msgid ""
"saddhindriyaṃ … pe … paññindriyaṃ bhāvitaṃ bahulīkataṃ amatogadhaṃ hoti "
"amataparāyaṇaṃ amatapariyosānaṃ."
msgstr ""
"the faculties of faith, energy, mindfulness, immersion, and wisdom, when "
"developed and cultivated, culminate, finish, and end in the deathless."

# With regards to the variants here, BB reads phassita, and this seems to be the standard reading in similar passages at Ps 1.3, Mnd 10, MN 70, etc.
#. VAR: aphassitaṃ → apassitaṃ (si, s1-3, km, mr) | aphusitaṃ (pts1)
msgctxt "sn48.44:2.3"
msgid ""
"Yesañhetaṃ, bhante, aññātaṃ assa adiṭṭhaṃ aviditaṃ asacchikataṃ aphassitaṃ "
"paññāya, te tattha paresaṃ saddhāya gaccheyyuṃ—"
msgstr ""
"There are those who have not known or seen or understood or realized or "
"experienced this with wisdom. They may rely on faith in this matter."

msgctxt "sn48.44:2.4"
msgid ""
"saddhindriyaṃ … pe … paññindriyaṃ bhāvitaṃ bahulīkataṃ amatogadhaṃ hoti "
"amataparāyaṇaṃ amatapariyosānaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn48.44:2.5"
msgid ""
"Yesañca kho etaṃ, bhante, ñātaṃ diṭṭhaṃ viditaṃ sacchikataṃ phassitaṃ "
"paññāya, nikkaṅkhā te tattha nibbicikicchā—"
msgstr ""
"But there are those who have known, seen, understood, realized, and "
"experienced this with wisdom. They have no doubts or uncertainties in this "
"matter."

msgctxt "sn48.44:2.6"
msgid ""
"saddhindriyaṃ … pe … paññindriyaṃ bhāvitaṃ bahulīkataṃ amatogadhaṃ hoti "
"amataparāyaṇaṃ amatapariyosānaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn48.44:2.7"
msgid ""
"Mayhañca kho etaṃ, bhante, ñātaṃ diṭṭhaṃ viditaṃ sacchikataṃ phassitaṃ "
"paññāya."
msgstr ""
"I have known, seen, understood, realized, and experienced this with wisdom."

msgctxt "sn48.44:2.8"
msgid ""
"Nikkaṅkhvāhaṃ tattha nibbicikiccho saddhindriyaṃ … pe … paññindriyaṃ "
"bhāvitaṃ bahulīkataṃ amatogadhaṃ hoti amataparāyaṇaṃ amatapariyosānan”ti."
msgstr ""
"I have no doubts or uncertainties that the faculties of faith, energy, "
"mindfulness, immersion, and wisdom, when developed and cultivated, "
"culminate, finish, and end in the deathless.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli5.222"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn48.44:3.1"
msgid "“Sādhu sādhu, sāriputta."
msgstr "“Good, good, Sāriputta!"

msgctxt "sn48.44:3.2"
msgid ""
"Yesañhetaṃ, sāriputta, aññātaṃ assa adiṭṭhaṃ aviditaṃ asacchikataṃ "
"aphassitaṃ paññāya, te tattha paresaṃ saddhāya gaccheyyuṃ—"
msgstr ""
"There are those who have not known or seen or understood or realized or "
"experienced this with wisdom. They may rely on faith in this matter."

msgctxt "sn48.44:3.3"
msgid ""
"saddhindriyaṃ bhāvitaṃ bahulīkataṃ amatogadhaṃ hoti amataparāyaṇaṃ "
"amatapariyosānaṃ … pe … paññindriyaṃ bhāvitaṃ bahulīkataṃ amatogadhaṃ hoti "
"amataparāyaṇaṃ amatapariyosānaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn48.44:3.4"
msgid ""
"Yesañca kho etaṃ, sāriputta, ñātaṃ diṭṭhaṃ viditaṃ sacchikataṃ phassitaṃ "
"paññāya, nikkaṅkhā te tattha nibbicikicchā—"
msgstr ""
"But there are those who have known, seen, understood, realized, and "
"experienced this with wisdom. They have no doubts or uncertainties that"

msgctxt "sn48.44:3.5"
msgid ""
"saddhindriyaṃ bhāvitaṃ bahulīkataṃ amatogadhaṃ hoti amataparāyaṇaṃ "
"amatapariyosānaṃ … pe … paññindriyaṃ bhāvitaṃ bahulīkataṃ amatogadhaṃ hoti "
"amataparāyaṇaṃ amatapariyosānan”ti."
msgstr ""
"the faculties of faith, energy, mindfulness, immersion, and wisdom, when "
"developed and cultivated, culminate, finish, and end in the deathless.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn48.44:3.6"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
